Linux 4.3 for Edison.

Status: boots, no i2c, no wifi, no bluetooth.

Installation
============
1. Build Yocto with this meta layer for 'edison' machine.
2. Download and unpack Edison installer for Linux.
3. Overwrite the following files

   u-boot-envs/edison-blank.bin             u-boot-envs/edison-blankcdc.bin
   u-boot-edison.bin                        u-boot-edison.bin                         
   u-boot-edison.img                        u-boot-edison.img                          
   core-image-minimal-edison-edison.ext4    edison-image-edison.ext4
   core-image-minimal-edison-edison.hddimg  edison-image-edison.hddimg

4. Run 'flashall.sh'.


